        <section id="future" class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="text-center mb-12">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl">An Unstable Equilibrium</h2>
                    <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg text-slate-600">The delicate balance of co-opetition is under threat. These key forces could fundamentally realign the entire tech ecosystem.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                    <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-200">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-red-100 text-red-600 mb-4">
                            <span class="text-2xl">⚖️</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">The Regulatory Hammer</h3>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">The DOJ's successful antitrust lawsuit against Google threatens to forcibly dissolve the $20B search deal with Apple. This is the most powerful external shock to the system, potentially severing a key financial link.</p>
                    </div>
                     <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-200">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 mb-4">
                            <span class="text-2xl">💡</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Technological Shifts</h3>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">The rise of Generative AI creates an opening for new search players to partner with Apple. Simultaneously, Apple's long-term push to design its own components (like microLEDs) aims to break its dependency on Samsung.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-200">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-green-100 text-green-600 mb-4">
                            <span class="text-2xl">🤝</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Evolving Alliances</h3>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">The Google-Samsung partnership is deepening, especially in AI, to create a stronger, more open alternative to Apple's "walled garden." This strengthens the anti-Apple axis but also contains its own potential for future friction.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
